https://openneuro.org/datasets/ds003481/versions/1.0.3
Task 4 Comprehension of metaphorical phrases (CMP)

Stimulus Info
Page 63 in the Metaphora PDF (UNAM Master Thesis by )

Examples: 
Figurative:               Literal:                  Absurd:
Corazon de piedra         Muro de piedra            Gelatina de piedra
(Heart of stone)          (Stone wall)              (Stone jelly)
Hermana dulce             La fruta dulce            Edificio dulce
(Sweet sister)            (Sweet fruit)             (Sweet building)

fMRI scanning parameters:
TR = 2
Volume = 250 (run 1), 250 (run 2)
Scan time = 500s for each run
Stimuli time = 500s
Run = 2
Subject = 18 (sub_064 - sub091)

Experimental design:
+ (0.5s) -> phrase (3.5s) -> + (5s) -> Question (3.5s) [12.5s in total]



